OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShetland often cloudy with some
OL,6,Fshowery rain at first, otherwise dry.
OL,7,FOrkney will have a dry day with broken
OL,8,Fcloud and sunny spells.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,11,Fsome brightness. Then the rest of the
OL,12,Fnight will be mainly dry and cloudy, a
OL,13,Flittle light rain possible across
OL,14,FOrkney later.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FA cloudy day with occasional
OL,17,Frain, tending become drier later in
OL,18,Fthe afternoon. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
